        "synopsis": {
            "value": "Third-rate theater company Minki is in crisis due to poor financials. Director Min-Ki (Jang Hyun-Sung) from the company decides to put on a performance of \"Hamlet\" as the company's final show. He persuades producer Chul-Goo (Park Chul-Min) to take part.\n\nThe curtain rises for \"Hamlet\" after many complications, but, during the performance, unintended mistakes and ad-libs become rampant.",
